---
import { LayoutDashboard, SendHorizontal, Users } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section id="product" class="py-14 sm:py-16">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div
			class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6 mb-10"
		>
			<div>
				<h2
					class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900"
				>
					Designed for Swiss SMEs, not for IT projects.
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-600 max-w-2xl">
					Whether you send 20 or 1,000 invoices per month, the portal
					keeps you compliant with PEPPOL and Swiss regulations
					without requiring an ERP system or custom integration.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div
				class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs text-slate-500"
				aria-label="Key product scope"
			>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
					<span
						class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
						aria-hidden="true"></span>
					<span>Outbound invoices at launch</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
					<span
						class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-500"
						aria-hidden="true"></span>
					<span>Inbound &amp; API planned on roadmap</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
			<div
				class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm"
			>
				<div
					class="mb-3 inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-blue-600"
				>
					<LayoutDashboard size={24} />
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
					Self-service portal
				</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-600">
					Create your account, configure company data, and start
					submitting invoices via a clean web interface – no
					onboarding project or IT team required.
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-xs text-slate-600">
					<li class="flex gap-2">
						<span
							class="mt-1 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
							aria-hidden="true"></span>
						Company metadata: VAT ID, registration, address, language
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-2">
						<span
							class="mt-1 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
							aria-hidden="true"></span>
						Dashboard with usage, status, and notifications
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div
				class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm"
			>
				<div
					class="mb-3 inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-blue-600"
				>
					<SendHorizontal size={24} />
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
					Flexible submission flows
				</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-600">
					Start with manual entry and grow into uploads and API as
					your volumes increase – all within the same portal and
					compliance framework.
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-xs text-slate-600">
					<li class="flex gap-2">
						<span
							class="mt-1 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
							aria-hidden="true"></span>
						Manual invoices with validation and instant status
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-2">
						<span
							class="mt-1 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
							aria-hidden="true"></span>
						File upload (XML, CSV, JSON – to be confirmed) for batches
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-2">
						<span
							class="mt-1 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
							aria-hidden="true"></span>
						Future: API submissions for Premium plans
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div
				class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm"
			>
				<div
					class="mb-3 inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-blue-600"
				>
					<Users size={24} />
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
					Built for SMEs, backed by experts
				</h3>
				<p class="mt-2 text-base text-slate-600">
					Taxera’s internal admin console monitors traffic, logs, and
					billing behind the scenes, so you focus on your business,
					not the plumbing.
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-xs text-slate-600">
					<li class="flex gap-2">
						<span
							class="mt-1 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
							aria-hidden="true"></span>
						Proactive monitoring of access point &amp; API performance
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-2">
						<span
							class="mt-1 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500"
							aria-hidden="true"></span>
						Manual reprocessing of failed invoices by Taxera staff
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
